
What Is This
------------

	This archive contains the required files to use Digi Booster 
	replayer library V2 by Sebastian Jedruszkiewicz

	In short, the Blitz Basic Includes that contains functions
        for playing Digi Booster Modules.
	
	Digi Booster is copyrighted 1997 by Tomasz & Waldemar Piasta.
	Digi Booster replayer library © Sebastian Jedruszkiewicz 1998

	I recomend That You DownLoad dbplayer.lib V2 from Aminet and read
	The Doc's For More Info on the lib & usage.


Requirements
------------

	- Blitz Basic

	- dbplayer.library V2 ( Aviable From Aminet )

	- AHI device version at least 4
	  AHI can be found on any aminet site And is copyrighted 1994-1997 
	  by Martin Blom

	- libraries that are used by AHI

	- at least MC68020 Processor

Install
-------

Copy all the files to the required location on your HD, and then you
will nead to re-compile You DEf-Libs the library included is lib number
7 - if this conflicts with you current setup you will nead to convert
the FD file....

